images.title: Paying respects on Anzac Day
images.caption: Paying respects on Anzac Day
images.desc: Today we commemorate Anzac Day, one of the country’s most important national occasions which marks the anniversary of the first major military action fought by Australian and New Zealand forces during the First World War.
